{"tid":103223,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做過正顎手術，您問我答","createTime":"2017-02-01T07:37:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T07:50:14.000Z","uid":35082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"88c06ae6463ae10402de2af2889752a4a21e3c5b","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:37:30.000Z","msg":"有片比大家睇，入面都解釋詳細<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12224008/%E8%87%B3fit%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3/%E9%A1%8E%E9%AA%A8%E7%9F%AF%E5%BD%A2%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F(%E4%BA%8C)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12224008%2F%25E8%2587%25B3fit%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%2F%25E9%25A1%258E%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%259F%25AF%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%259F%28%25E4%25BA%258C%29&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=f909b5e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12224008%2F%25E8%2587%25B3fit%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%2F%25E9%25A1%258E%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%259F%25AF%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%259F%28%25E4%25BA%258C%29&h=da036a73\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12224008/%E8%87%B3fit%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3/%E9%A1%8E%E9%AA%A8%E7%9F%AF%E5%BD%A2%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F(%E4%BA%8C)</a><br />\n<br />\n呢條片有術過程，未做唔好睇住，會嚇親<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12224007/%E8%87%B3fit%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3/%E9%A1%8E%E9%AA%A8%E7%9F%AF%E5%BD%A2%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F(%E4%B8%89)\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12224007%2F%25E8%2587%25B3fit%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%2F%25E9%25A1%258E%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%259F%25AF%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%259F%28%25E4%25B8%2589%29&d=W%2FrRVga79FgW6ojUxQ3KLaWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=4c7bd1c6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fprogram%2F12224007%2F%25E8%2587%25B3fit%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%2F%25E9%25A1%258E%25E9%25AA%25A8%25E7%259F%25AF%25E5%25BD%25A2%25E9%2587%258D%25E7%2594%259F%28%25E4%25B8%2589%29&h=6991d0e7\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/program/12224007/%E8%87%B3fit%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3/%E9%A1%8E%E9%AA%A8%E7%9F%AF%E5%BD%A2%E9%87%8D%E7%94%9F(%E4%B8%89)</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有任何關於正顎手術嘅嘢都可以問<br />\n利申：只做下顎，仲箍緊牙，希望幫到大家"},{"pid":"48a2d56c55cb2348b371c40d0b1960976f19140f","tid":103223,"uid":35323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:39:57.000Z","msg":"幾錢?<br />\n係邊度做?<br />\n點解要做?<br />\n做咗之後點?<br />\n要幾耐時間復原?"},{"pid":"d33978b0e09a13aa102956eedbcd30b35080ec4c","tid":103223,"uid":54927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:44:17.000Z","msg":"做完應該成個人唔同哂<br />\n可唔可以影做之前 之後黎睇"},{"pid":"dd5e951ef63a0dff462dcceaa08bb2db4913ddd2","tid":103223,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:49:31.000Z","msg":"以前曾經想做..私家十幾萬 公立8萬 太貴無做到<br />\n<br />\n唔係倒及自問1定係靚仔"},{"pid":"5ac067fd91b1574504f9ca95ae05b0e7dba96331","tid":103223,"uid":32461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:51:49.000Z","msg":"為左靚先做？<br />\n定真係影響咬合或者其他健康問題？"},{"pid":"d28f8195d5f0856c5a6816b1c1355120c69fd79c","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:55:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>幾錢?<br />\n係邊度做?<br />\n點解要做?<br />\n做咗之後點?<br />\n要幾耐時間復原?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老母喺公務員，淨喺比住院費<br />\n本身倒及牙，箍完牙會嚴重咗。上下棚牙合唔埋，放得落一隻手指<br />\n做完正面冇太大分別，但側邊好明顯，好睇好多<br />\n醫生話我復原得快，2星期已經食到通粉。不過做完半年，仲有少少後遺症"},{"pid":"896a4ed8a40765ec31e29144d8d9832f82125571","tid":103223,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:55:54.000Z","msg":"不過我都想問下由求醫到做完手術個過程"},{"pid":"f2f8c512409264368d68020b4c41bf9a5e1741d0","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:58:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做完應該成個人唔同哂<br />\n可唔可以影做之前 之後黎睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一影相會自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://beautynews.fashionguide.com.tw/i/forum_topic/00/00/75/00007571/201405241448580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeautynews.fashionguide.com.tw%2Fi%2Fforum_topic%2F00%2F00%2F75%2F00007571%2F201405241448580.jpg&h=ac4811fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張上網搵，我效果同佢差唔多"},{"pid":"5d285b785268b429d692921f4f23691873ea9e4b","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T07:59:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>為左靚先做？<br />\n定真係影響咬合或者其他健康問題？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n靚同咬合係最大原因"},{"pid":"027ae935407f7bf78cd9f498924ba2809fb3c4d9","tid":103223,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:01:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>做完應該成個人唔同哂<br />\n可唔可以影做之前 之後黎睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一影相會自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://beautynews.fashionguide.com.tw/i/forum_topic/00/00/75/00007571/201405241448580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeautynews.fashionguide.com.tw%2Fi%2Fforum_topic%2F00%2F00%2F75%2F00007571%2F201405241448580.jpg&h=ac4811fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張上網搵，我效果同佢差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你唔係同一個人黎架下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼形唔同條眉又唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7db13f22d1b28f47079141568bd0ebde9f50d5","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:01:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>以前曾經想做..私家十幾萬 公立8萬 太貴無做到<br />\n<br />\n唔係倒及自問1定係靚仔</blockquote><br />\n菲臘牙科會平d，但而家唔知仲收唔收<br />\n如果真係嚴重，我都建議照做"},{"pid":"dd7d3965ad664f8d2f4cd7d86e7de617227eba4b","tid":103223,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:02:33.000Z","msg":"醫生有無講過點解會有倒及? <br />\n<br />\n我屋企人都無淨得我有"},{"pid":"0e9d9ec094825c17ef9e0d0a26b35aaed61306b6","tid":103223,"uid":7854,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前曾經想做..私家十幾萬 公立8萬 太貴無做到<br />\n<br />\n唔係倒及自問1定係靚仔</blockquote><br />\n菲臘牙科會平d，但而家唔知仲收唔收<br />\n如果真係嚴重，我都建議照做</blockquote><br />\n錢真係係最大因素"},{"pid":"534205980235ac0f88088557847fcadbbcbd87ae","tid":103223,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:03:30.000Z","msg":"同埋菲蠟以前爬過文<br />\n<br />\n好似係學生做 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a37169676b3a8f99669e39d3117826aad6e1f51","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:04:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過我都想問下由求醫到做完手術個過程</blockquote><br />\n我箍牙前醫生都有講定話有機會要做正顎<br />\n箍咗冇耐就肯定要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0411fc88721db52b22a9f2c6a94e573900a0804","tid":103223,"uid":7854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:04:22.000Z","msg":"做完手術而家咬合會唔會有後遺 (唔可以太大力咬合?"},{"pid":"87cf755ae3036fe69e4ccded0197cf8640d254c9","tid":103223,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>以前曾經想做..私家十幾萬 公立8萬 太貴無做到<br />\n<br />\n唔係倒及自問1定係靚仔</blockquote><br />\n菲臘牙科會平d，但而家唔知仲收唔收<br />\n如果真係嚴重，我都建議照做</blockquote><br />\n我唔嚴重 仲有左右唔對稱 但左右對稱番倒及會嚴重左<br />\n有個表哥仲西利 真係遺傳基因.."},{"pid":"7e2dd20d5ffe51ecf341f1e559db854bcf448b18","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:05:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>醫生有無講過點解會有倒及? <br />\n<br />\n我屋企人都無淨得我有</blockquote><br />\n我係遺傳問題，因為老豆都有"},{"pid":"15a1402f8abfca8427ee91ce51bcc7ab70f0c5b9","tid":103223,"uid":25237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:09:15.000Z","msg":"係咪會痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 今個暑假做"},{"pid":"ed4f020ebf745f91abf86fb9336e4b4961e4d319","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:09:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做完手術而家咬合會唔會有後遺 (唔可以太大力咬合?</blockquote><br />\n後遺就一定有。我下巴感覺會差咗，食嘢有時污糟咗都唔知，同埋會容易咗流口水。不過都唔算好大影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1666f869b27c198b1aa32c2bfc6b8ee9a3339d6","tid":103223,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:10:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>做完應該成個人唔同哂<br />\n可唔可以影做之前 之後黎睇</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一影相會自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://beautynews.fashionguide.com.tw/i/forum_topic/00/00/75/00007571/201405241448580.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbeautynews.fashionguide.com.tw%2Fi%2Fforum_topic%2F00%2F00%2F75%2F00007571%2F201405241448580.jpg&h=ac4811fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張上網搵，我效果同佢差唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你唔係同一個人黎架下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼形唔同條眉又唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇得出係同1個人 人靚左 <br />\n成個世界會唔同哂"},{"pid":"9f3653fb133c356c5468d9bcd3cb607f8af4ac62","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:12:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係咪會痛到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申 今個暑假做</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實唔痛架，最慘係頭一兩日成口血同冇得食嘢<br />\n加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw巴打邊間做？"},{"pid":"8d242d98763818a95ad9d3a7a0e70a247eb13e7d","tid":103223,"uid":35082,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你唔係同一個人黎架下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼形唔同條眉又唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇得出係同1個人 人靚左 <br />\n成個世界會唔同哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我做完手術d朋友仲認到我，但佢哋都話好睇咗。<br />\n有d朋友仲問我係咪整咗容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20247a603c0ba5a6241500d579fd61dbefc9ef5e","tid":103223,"uid":22700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:26:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌你唔係同一個人黎架下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n眼形唔同條眉又唔同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇得出係同1個人 人靚左 <br />\n成個世界會唔同哂</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁我做完手術d朋友仲認到我，但佢哋都話好睇咗。<br />\n有d朋友仲問我係咪整咗容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實都算整容"},{"pid":"2fe8934cc3efe6de20306557a43208822ac0784d","tid":103223,"uid":64767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-01T08:45:31.000Z","msg":"想整上顎要幾錢? 風險會唔會大啲?"}]}